Shahla KhatunNational Professor

Shahla Khatun is a Bangladeshi physician and National Professor.[1]

Career[edit]
Professor Shahla Khatun, MBBS, FCPS, FRCOG (London) is a gynecologist. She has served IPGMR, currently Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University as a professor and head of department, Department of Obstretics and Gynecology. She was inducted as a National Professor by the government of Bangladesh in 2011.[2] She also taught at the Bangladesh Medical College.[3]
